[[/div]]
----
[[div class="email"]]
[[div class="tofrom"]]

**To:** ##red|You## [[span style="color: gray; font-size: 70%;"]]11:26PM (4 minutes ago)[[/span]]
**From:** Chris Aster [[span style="color: gray; font-size: 70%;"]]<@<caster@site7.scp>@>[[/span]]
**Subject:** Doing okay?
[[/div]]
----

Hey. Hope you got back to base safe after the service ended. I didn't hear the Condor taking off, but it was raining pretty hard, so you know. It was a nice funeral, I think. She would've liked it. Never was the type for big fancy events.

Anyhow, I was writing to share this. We found it on a USB among her possessions. Normally they have RAISA techs scan this sort of thing to make sure it's not anomalous, but I think they didn't even bother this time. If Maria Jones wanted to sneak something past the Foundation, she would've done it before she died, and probably would've gotten away with it too.

Sorry, got distracted again. Evie's taking it pretty hard. Take a look once you get back on-site. I think you'll appreciate it.

[[>]]

Chris Aster
[[span style="color: gray; font-size: 70%;"]]RAISA Assistant Director[[/span]]
[[/>]]
